{"id":421108,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/12/ngocn-披着化肥袋的羊！？中国孩子都是怎么被折腾的/","date":"2015-12-11T11:33:12Z","modified":"2015-12-11T16:00:36Z","title":"NGOCN | 披着化肥袋的羊！？中国孩子都是怎么被折腾的","content":"<p><strong>关注NGOCN，公益视野从此大不同</strong><br />\n<strong> 原创·责编：鹿柴</strong></p>\n<p>今天爆出来一条新闻：</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.30.00.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-421109\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.30.00.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-12-11 at 上午3.30.00\" width=\"550\" height=\"259\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.30.00.png 639w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.30.00-300x141.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>人民日报的评论文章《杜绝“造盆景式”的作秀扶贫》：在不少贫困地区仍存在着“造盆景”“垒大户”等重“面子工程”的扶贫做法。有个地方，<strong>为了让上级考察时看到自己的扶贫成绩，派一些小学生披着装化肥用的白塑料袋，趴在领导路过的山坡上</strong>。领导远远望去，山坡上尽是“美羊羊”，大加赞许。地方干部“喜洋洋”，皆大欢喜。</p>\n<p>这条新闻一出来，网友们反应几乎都是：what！！？披化肥袋装羊！！？这是什么新式cosplay课程吗？</p>\n<p>说到装羊，今年初才有媒体爆出内蒙由于草原受到严重破坏，留下众多煤坑，只好在草皮上放仿真羊模型，蒙骗游人。一个1：1仿真羊在淘宝上也不过卖198一只，这些贫困县的孩子难道是冲话费送的吗？</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.31.18.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-421110\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.31.18.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-12-11 at 上午3.31.18\" width=\"550\" height=\"267\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.31.18.png 641w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.31.18-300x146.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><br />\n为了满足领导们的“喜洋洋”，在一些地区，折腾孩子仿佛已经成为性价比最高的方法了。</p>\n<p>早些年，某地要求中小学生要向过往车辆敬礼，当地教育部门称，<strong>这是在全县范围内推广的礼仪方式，全县所有中小学生都会向过路车辆敬礼</strong>，一是表示对驾驶员的尊重，二是防止安全事故发生。</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.32.42.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-421111\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.32.42.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-12-11 at 上午3.32.42\" width=\"299\" height=\"177\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.32.42.png 299w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.32.42-80x48.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 299px) 100vw, 299px\" /></a></p>\n<p>还有报道，某地小学在举行“迎元旦·绿色安全行”主题活动，孩子们冒雨起舞，为台上穿雨衣撑伞的领导表演节目。</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.33.18.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-421112\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.33.18.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-12-11 at 上午3.33.18\" width=\"547\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.33.18.png 547w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.33.18-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 547px) 100vw, 547px\" /></a></p>\n<p>活动当天气象台发布了沿海大风警报和天气预报，天气阴有小雨，白天最高温度12℃~14℃。据该校教导处徐老师介绍，<strong>舞蹈时间只有三四分钟，“穿雨衣也没法跳舞。”至于给领导打伞，她说，“大人没办法穿，也不能淋雨啊？”</strong></p>\n<p>当然这是几年前的新闻，现在的情况是这样的：</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.34.04.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-421113\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.34.04.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-12-11 at 上午3.34.04\" width=\"550\" height=\"416\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.34.04.png 633w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.34.04-300x227.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><br />\n好吧……领导您身体弱，比小学生还弱……</p>\n<p>有时候不知道是不是该庆幸领导身体弱，如果体魄强健的话，是不是会像这样：</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.35.12.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-421114\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.35.12.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-12-11 at 上午3.35.12\" width=\"550\" height=\"240\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.35.12.png 624w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.35.12-300x131.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>回顾这些年的社会新闻，孩子们确实就像山上的“美羊羊”一样，配合着各种政绩、面子工程折腾，特别是小学生，因为他们听话，因为他们信任老师、信任学校、信任领导，披上化肥袋到山坡上趴一会，对他们来说，似乎真的也算不上怎样的大事，对于领导来说，自然也是“喜洋洋”的。</p>\n<p>但我们永远都不该忘记，21年前的12月8日，发生在领导们和一群听话的孩子身上的事情。</p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.36.02.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-421115\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.36.02.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-12-11 at 上午3.36.02\" width=\"467\" height=\"319\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.36.02.png 467w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/12/Screen-Shot-2015-12-11-at-上午3.36.02-300x205.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 467px) 100vw, 467px\" /></a></p>\n<p>以一首歌结束:</p>\n<p>周云蓬 | 中国孩子</p>\n<p>视频<a href=\"http://v.qq.com/page/s/0/b/s0011ypbfbb.html\" target=\"_blank\">地址</a></p>\n<p>[youtube]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m7XbIhypZCo[/youtube]</p>\n","author":996,"categories":[18270,18269,9203,10466],"tags":[28907,10755,9872,10452,9364,12979]}